Diagnostic Retrieval Systems Incsaid it has made an offer to acquire, through a wholly ownedunit, all outstanding shares of Rospatch Corp's common stockfor 22 dlrs a share cash, or about 53 mln dlrs.    DRS, a warfare systems producer, said it would make thetransaction through a cash tender offer for all, but not lessthan 51 pct, of Rospatch's outstanding common stock followed bya merger with Rospatch, a labels, high technology and woodproducer, at the same purchase price per share.    DRS said the deal is subject to approval by the Rospatchboard, and the tender offer expires on March 6, 1986. Reuter&#3;